Rustic Italian Themed Wedding

Italy was the inspiration for this week’s featured wedding, and we have to say it was one of the most inspirational and creative weddings we have helped to plan this year.

The location: The Calegari Vineyards in Healdsburg. This exclusive vineyard only holds about eight weddings a year, and luckily for us, we have assisted with almost all of them!
